{"tid":555901,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"肚痛忍屎忍到差d暈咗","createTime":"2018-02-10T03:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T12:14:47.000Z","uid":60219,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c3ee2e38c5cee1e0244ec80c8ffd2842862d9d7e","tid":555901,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:30:02.000Z","msg":"今朝要考試，短短哋考個半鐘<br />\n<br />\n明明朝早出門之前已經屙咗一大篤，但開考半個鐘之後都突發性肚痛，因為我有腸胃焦慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有諗過中途去屙，但又驚做唔曬份卷，所以決定死忍爛忍<br />\n<br />\n考緊果陣，有五/六次便意好似海嘯咁無預警突然湧上嚟，每次我都鎖住丹田收緊菊花，一諗到係試場瀨咗屎搞到全場疏散果種情況就勉強忍得到<br />\n<br />\n成份卷潦到好似蘇東坡飲醉酒寫草書咁都無辦法，臨完場5分鐘終於做完諗住早走，個考場主任好似睇得出我急屎，陰陰嘴笑開咪講&quot;考試剩餘5分鐘，考生不得離開試場&quot;，我仆你個街，聽日就走去你office門口屙返篤屎<br />\n<br />\n收卷班友個個都有柏金遜症咁既款，手震震妺下妹下慢慢收卷，收到我果份我差d想即刻屙出嚟然後塞入佢哋把口比佢哋慢慢妹<br />\n<br />\n散場之後附近廁所一係排曬隊，一係個屎塔污糟到好似有隻牛入去爆完石咁，搞到我要行多幾分鐘先搵到個乾淨又無人既廁所，就好似一絲曙光咁充滿希望<br />\n<br />\n屙出嚟果刻腳都震撚埋，仲有兩秒好似腦缺氧咁視線模糊咗；屙完回頭望下個屎塔，篤屎既顏色就好似菠蘿包，都唔知尋晚食完咩嚟先屙咗舊咁既妖孽出嚟，must kill it before it lays eggs，你老味！"},{"pid":"014423efd829553fa76a555acec103be184b7ab8","tid":555901,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"菠蘿包咁既色 應該好靚 想見識下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6a4064988d81a308dca6ebb4a578d66d25a097","tid":555901,"uid":60219,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"014423efd829553fa76a555acec103be184b7ab8","tid":555901,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"菠蘿包咁既色 應該好靚 想見識下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:41:55.000Z","msg":"平時d屎好深色，今次唔知做咩發曬光咁"},{"pid":"9864481cba513d6e07793d8c8c35a9448209bf80","tid":555901,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:09:54.000Z","msg":"巴打好好笑"},{"pid":"ce6d634f45e24995e02831cac8d471955ac5eba8","tid":555901,"uid":48609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:13:30.000Z","msg":"那兒來的"},{"pid":"0dd6ca7b8f7ebd6738eb7736c152cff67a81b7cb","tid":555901,"uid":60219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"屌，又肚痛屙多次<br />\n一陣up圖比大家觀摩"},{"pid":"2bd66b9374634d06e5e50c77e7dd78a9f9c0b2da","tid":555901,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"014423efd829553fa76a555acec103be184b7ab8","tid":555901,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"菠蘿包咁既色 應該好靚 想見識下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:56:20.000Z","msg":"慎入<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.imgur.com/a/IcnJ2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.imgur.com%2Fa%2FIcnJ2&d=h3oADuDJK3jSendkQNSAcQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=2247afec\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.imgur.com/a/IcnJ2</a><br />\n<br />\n可惜呢次都無頭先咁光鮮亮麗"},{"pid":"ed53b02a56b9cf44ca2f852e922eeb6e50a4b635","tid":555901,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>菠蘿包咁既色 應該好靚 想見識下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>平時d屎好深色，今次唔知做咩發曬光咁</blockquote><br />\n條腸D分秘"},{"pid":"48760c0a9dc777b52ca3c4cebdd1438e6a252608","tid":555901,"uid":170786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"more"},{"pid":"ff1813b8da557316f62ff7356021522ff96b24e7","tid":555901,"uid":90605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:06:45.000Z","msg":"More"},{"pid":"4da1210c7e96a27809c0146c665a7a2e7184c3c4","tid":555901,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48760c0a9dc777b52ca3c4cebdd1438e6a252608","tid":555901,"uid":170786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"more"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:24:02.000Z","msg":"你要more乜先"},{"pid":"8054e4f131e93c4693997c1949d10044e75c